How thoughtful and farsighted Madam is.

575
00:35:53,840 --> 00:35:55,960
I promise I won't let her down.

576
00:36:46,480 --> 00:36:48,340
Whether I can change my fate or not

577
00:36:48,880 --> 00:36:50,550
depends on this one move.

578
00:37:42,150 --> 00:37:43,960
As I expected,

579
00:37:45,090 --> 00:37:48,760
you can't recreate
a complete Myriad Blight Formation,

580
00:37:51,020 --> 00:37:52,320
but you can

581
00:37:53,880 --> 00:37:56,150
assist me in absorbing power.

582
00:37:56,590 --> 00:37:58,550
The power is not enough, though.

583
00:38:00,510 --> 00:38:02,590
I'll take you to the Dragon Cave

584
00:38:02,960 --> 00:38:05,420
where you can take in
plenty of dragon power.

585
00:38:07,590 --> 00:38:09,150
I, Quan Jingting,

586
00:38:10,880 --> 00:38:13,440
will rise again.

587
00:38:17,630 --> 00:38:19,070
My rebellious son...

